    "description": "Single Source of Truth (SSOT) for all BukuWarung payment transactions. Consolidates Payment In, Payment Out, PPOB, QRIS, QRIS-Retail, and SALDO. Each row = one payment attempt (bw_order_id). product_type determines populated columns; status_v2 encodes full lifecycle; transaction_date (WIB) is partition key.",
